divs: sighting detailsthis is same siting but date\time on previous posting is erroneous. my apologies for not setting the time zone correctly. i reported it the same night i saw it a few hours after seeing it tonight, thursday november 4 at approx dusk, 6 pm (sunset was at 5:44 pm), nothing else is changed, this siting corroborates the previous siting earlier today in southern california, that description matches what i saw (my corrected vision is pretty good, i would not say excellent), i had the right glasses on and the weather here was exactly what the other witness reported, warm, dry, no wind, very still.
